{"tid":2443696,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"杭州男「三角內褲」狂被偷！兇手竟然是同村的男子","createTime":"2021-03-12T08:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T08:36:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51fd08fc18de95dfee4a88e86696a77e8ee8b9b5","tid":2443696,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／李艾庭報導<br />\n<br />\n浙江省杭州市一名袁先生，從今年2月份開始，就發現自己的內褲離奇失蹤，每次晚上換洗下來、晾在院子，隔天就會消失，奇怪的是，家裡的人明明都一起曬衣服，但兒子的平口內褲卻沒有不見，前前後後被偷了十幾條內褲，袁先生受不了，決定裝監視器，結果兇手竟然是一名住在同村莊男子，而背後的原因更讓他傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/12/3061770-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F12%2F3061770-PH.jpg&h=499e2269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《搜狐新聞》報導，家住雙浦鎮蘭溪口村的袁先生，從2月份開始，洗好晾在自家院子的三角內褲，經過一個晚上就會不見，只剩下空衣架，奇怪的是，全家人的內褲都一起曬，但只有他的內褲不見，兒子的平口內褲從沒有被偷。<br />\n<br />\n被偷了十幾條內褲，袁先生受不了，決定在院子裝監視器，並到雙浦派出所報案。警方透過監視器進行追查，終於找到偷內褲的嫌疑人小張。<br />\n<br />\n原來小張本來是隔壁村人，因為家中拆遷，目前租屋在蘭溪口村，平常上下班都會經過袁先生家，看到晾在外面的男性三角內褲，便起了賊心，只要發現一樓燈黑、二樓燈亮，就會走進院子偷內褲，偷回家後也會再洗一次，等到穿舊才丟掉。<br />\n<br />\n至於為何只偷袁先生內褲，小張自稱有奇怪癖好，只喜歡男性的三角內褲，覺得穿上後有莫名快感。而經警方調查，小張前前後後共偷內褲15次、共15條，依法逮捕小張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=909385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D909385&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=e58c13cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D909385&h=138c1a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=909385</a>"},{"pid":"793852286b9b428c55950a70fc716911e14029f1","tid":2443696,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"GAY版八寶齋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/378800000786932803/5cc832865bec32252fe7e9e7cd851c66.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F378800000786932803%2F5cc832865bec32252fe7e9e7cd851c66.jpeg&h=c7ac2682&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05663ca9e3e248269422b83e8e1c921bee5525d4","tid":2443696,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"變態假面"},{"pid":"263a0899fbd2b529ab33db9640d605ab5f513115","tid":2443696,"uid":282626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小張自稱有奇怪癖好，只喜歡男性的三角內褲，覺得穿上後有莫名快感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔射埋上去條底褲、再物歸原主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385d8bb1cebdedf9cc1b550cb4465894911b86a7","tid":2443696,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qyJS59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qyJS59.png&h=24fa9350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c80d6970908b8640a98dc008f1e96d34674990e6","tid":2443696,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"無殺人都比人叫兇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}